%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor RM as Resource Manager

participant UI as Resource Plan Approval UI
participant BFF as Execution BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant RMS as Resource Management Service
participant ADP as Service Adapter
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

RM->>UI: Open submitted resource plan
UI->>BFF: Load resource plan details
BFF->>ORCH: Get approval view
ORCH->>RMS: Fetch resource plan
RMS->>READDB: Query resource plan and allocation summary
READDB-->>RMS: Plan details
RMS-->>ORCH: Approval response
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show plan summary

alt Approve
    RM->>UI: Approve resource plan
    UI->>BFF: Submit approval
    BFF->>ORCH: Start approval flow
    ORCH->>RMS: Approve and activate allocations
    RMS->>PRIMARYDB: Update resource plan status = Approved
    RMS->>PRIMARYDB: Update resource allocations = Active
    PRIMARYDB-->>RMS: Approval success
    ORCH->>ADP: Notify team members and timesheet integration
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish ResourcePlanApproved Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show approved state
else Send Back / Reject
    RM->>UI: Send back / reject plan
    UI->>BFF: Submit decision
    BFF->>ORCH: Start send back / reject flow
    ORCH->>RMS: Update resource plan decision
    RMS->>PRIMARYDB: Update resource plan status
    PRIMARYDB-->>RMS: Decision saved
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish ResourcePlanReturned Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show returned state
end